Title: AdvGen Contact Manager
Description: This project is a simple contact manager which is using wpf.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
This is a simple contact management system. Moreover, it supports the export format of AdvGen Contact
So you can import the contact from your android phone. Moreover, we are aiming to create a MVC Framework for WPF in this project.
